{
  "stem": "16395.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Right away, we had yellow stars in a yellow band on the-- on the arm, on the right side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was right away in the end of 1939.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we had the rations, we didn't have enough to eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother used to stay in line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I figured, why should she stay in the line?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I used to stay every day in the line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not ?] once, I stayed a half a night, and when it came to me, they said that they don't have any more bread.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In 19-- the beginning of '40, I think it was like in January-- it was on a Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I stayed in the line and I came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother was in bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, she woke up, and she says, oh, I forgot to [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, no, today is Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I realized right away that she caught the typhus fever, because this was going around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "People were dying like the flies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the synagogue, what I said, from this shul, they used to take out 20 a day, 30 a day, because this is very, very contagious.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If once has it-- one has it in the family, the whole family gets it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What should I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I ran.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One thing I'll tell you, before I start out-- when the war out-- was out, I was a child, but I grew up in one year, I think 30 years.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew how to take care of myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew how to be wise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew when-- when to do anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I grew up very, very fast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was, that time, already, I think, 14.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway, I went to the doctor, and the doctor came up.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
